{#

Render resource wrappers for applicable command pairs.

Context
--------------------------------
resource_wrappers (Iterable[gladiator.prepare.resource_wrapper.PreparedResourceWrapper]): Wrappers to render

Globals
--------------------------------
options (gladiator.options.Options): Merged CLI and config file options
constants (gladiator.generate.constants.Constants): Constants for shared use
